256
00:13:19,765 --> 00:13:22,436
That's a load of crap!
You're full of crap!

257
00:13:22,521 --> 00:13:24,065
You guys tell him too.

258
00:13:24,148 --> 00:13:27,279
You'll never be seein'
each other again anyway.

259
00:13:27,363 --> 00:13:30,494
You all porked her! You're Shiro's dad!

260
00:13:30,578 --> 00:13:32,081
You're Rika's dad!

261
